Creating stack https://docs.aws.amazon.com/cli/latest/reference/cloudformation/create-stack.html
aws cloudformation create-stack --stack-name week-11-demo --template-body file://asg.yml (in case you use aws profile, need to provide --profile <name of the profile>)

Updating stack https://docs.aws.amazon.com/cli/latest/reference/cloudformation/update-stack.html
aws cloudformation update-stack --stack-name week-11-demo --template-body file://asg.yml

Deleting stack https://docs.aws.amazon.com/cli/latest/reference/cloudformation/delete-stack.html
aws cloudformation delete-stack --stack-name week-11-demo

Validating your yml or json file https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AWSCloudFormation/latest/UserGuide/using-cfn-validate-template.html
aws cloudformation validate-template --template-body file://asg.yml

A yaml validator https://codebeautify.org/yaml-validator

A aws troubleshooting blog https://aws.amazon.com/premiumsupport/knowledge-center/cloudformation-template-validation/

How to connect to a private instance via bastion on Windows or Mac & Linux
https://docs.bitnami.com/aws-templates/infrastructure/lamp-production-ready/get-started/connect-ssh/
or
https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/security/securely-connect-to-linux-instances-running-in-a-private-amazon-vpc/

How to use Fn::FindInMap - how to learn about CloudFormation
https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AWSCloudFormation/latest/UserGuide/intrinsic-function-reference-findinmap.html

How to copy and paste without memorizing anything by referring to AWS CloudFormation documents
https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AWSCloudFormation/latest/UserGuide/quickref-autoscaling.html

How to have subnets calculated 
https://www.davidc.net/sites/default/subnets/subnets.html

Troubleshooting Could not open a connection to your authentication agent
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/17846529/could-not-open-a-connection-to-your-authentication-agent
eval `ssh-agent -s`

